to drop the
investigation of Michael Flynn.

06:13.906 --> 06:19.178 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The fired national security
adviser is under
scrutiny over his Russia ties.

06:19.212 --> 06:24.117 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CNN and The Wall Street Journal
report that
Comey is expected to tell that
to the Senate

06:24.150 --> 06:27.420 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Intelligence Committee as early
as next week.

06:27.453 --> 06:32.091 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
