climate accord,
the 2015 agreement signed by
nearly 200 nations

18:55.334 --> 18:59.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to reduce the carbon emissions
that are driving
climate change.

18:59.071 --> 19:03.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The U.S. is the second biggest
emitter of
those greenhouse gasses
globally.

19:03.909 --> 19:07.880 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
William Brangham has the story
for our weekly
segment on the Leading Edge of
science.

19:07.913 --> 19:10.582 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
You're going to find out very
soon.

19:10.616 --> 19:13.752 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: It's a
decision being awaited
around the world.

19:13.785 --> 19:18.690 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
